phylo3D.tools
Class NCBItoNH

java.lang.Object
  phylo3D.tools.Tool
      phylo3D.tools.ToolWithNHOutput
          phylo3D.tools.NCBItoNH
public class NCBItoNH
extends ToolWithNHOutput

Loads the NCBI tree from serialized file into TreeNCBI which can then be manipulated (narrowed) before it is printed to a NH or NHX file. The options when calling the program are: --narrowTo=node where node is NCBI taxonomy ID (obligatory) --sequenceName=T or S, where T: NCBI taxonomy IDs and S: NCBI scientific species names (obligatory) --internalNodes=Y or N, where Y:internal node data is included in output and N: data not included (obligatory) --outputFormat=NH or NHX (obligatory) outputFile (obligatory)

Author:
Tim Hughes (Computational Biology Unit - University of Bergen - Norway)
